* "I'm trying to pay but it's not going through" could imply intent "troubleshoot\_payment\_issue"
* "The app keeps saying 'payment failed'" could imply intent "troubleshoot\_payment\_issue"
* "I've tried several times but it still doesn't work" could imply intent "troubleshoot\_payment\_issue"

Answer:
